## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible factors affecting cognitive development. Additionally, the influence of emerging technologies and digital media on cognitive development in middle childhood was not extensively covered in the sources reviewed. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these modern influences.